# Bandsaw Training Checklist

[ ] Useful PPE - hearing protection. No gloves!
[ ] Show location of stop buttons and estop in the workspace
[ ] Check machine and work area are safe
[ ] Show pusher sticks, fence, and tilt mechanism
[ ] Explain the basics of blade types and tension - not too taught or there's a risk of damage to tires
[ ] Demonstrate a simple cut
[ ] Have trainee do a simple cut
[ ] Demonstrate cleaning the inside of the machine after use
